00:01:40,909 --> 00:01:42,709
Impressive indeed.

23
00:01:44,030 --> 00:01:45,830
My turn now.

24
00:02:05,678 --> 00:02:08,589
 
Yi Ren, I won.

25
00:02:16,030 --> 00:02:20,869
Hold out your hand. Now!

26
00:02:41,590 --> 00:02:45,190
I agreed to this duel
thinking you'd gained some ambition.

27
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:49,590
Yet instead of rigorous training,
you resort to tricks.

28
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:54,870
Well, Yi Ren, don't get worked up.

29
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:57,389
Right now, the martial world is in turmoil.

30
00:02:57,389 --> 00:03:00,870
In martial arts, there's always someone better.

31
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:06,389
Besides, isn't it a good thing
if our heir is a bit smarter?

32
00:03:06,389 --> 00:03:09,710
I won through wits within the rules.

33
00:03:09,710 --> 00:03:13,389
Father, Mother, even Yi Ren
must concede defeat, right?

34
00:03:13,389 --> 00:03:15,629
Yes. Loss must be acknowledged.

35
00:03:19,990 --> 00:03:23,550
Nonsense. How could sophistry
be the righteous path?

36
00:03:23,550 --> 00:03:26,750
How shall we compare lightness skills next?

37
00:03:26,750 --> 00:03:30,230
Whoever grabs the flower first wins.

38
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:49,990
Is Qiu Shui doing it on purpose?

39
00:03:49,990 --> 00:03:52,149
He's trying to anger Yi Ren?

40
00:04:00,090 --> 00:04:02,230
One, two, three, four.

41
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:16,869
What new trickery is this?

42
00:04:19,149 --> 00:04:25,149
Qiu Shui, must all your duels
involve underhanded methods?

43
00:04:25,149 --> 00:04:28,509
Our Xiao family's prestige
comes from genuine skills.

44
00:04:28,509 --> 00:04:31,029
Your sophistry isn't the righteous way.

45
00:04:31,029 --> 00:04:33,509
Where's your respect for our family rules?

46
00:04:36,230 --> 00:04:40,110
If Qiu Shui persists, I'm afraid
Yi Ren will truly lose his temper.

47
00:04:40,110 --> 00:04:42,430
Another punishment awaits him.

48
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:48,230
Relax. Hasn't Qiu Shui always
made trouble but avoided consequences?

49
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:58,790
A duel tests true skill. No more tricks!

50
00:04:59,550 --> 00:05:01,350
Okay.

51
00:05:15,110 --> 00:05:16,910
Wonderful!

52
00:05:19,310 --> 00:05:21,389
Wonderful duel.

53
00:05:21,389 --> 00:05:23,509
Mother's Triple Shameless Moves?

54
00:05:23,509 --> 00:05:27,269
She taught Qiu Shui her signature move.

55
00:05:36,350 --> 00:05:38,150
Yi Ren, watch out!

56
00:06:06,389 --> 00:06:10,269
- Qiu Shui's reversing sword techniques?
- Isn't that reckless?

57
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:32,350
- Qiu Shui, are you okay?
- Qiu Shui.

58
00:06:32,350 --> 00:06:34,389
- Did you hit your head?
- Qiu Shui.

59
00:06:34,389 --> 00:06:36,189
Are you alright, Qiu Shui?

60
00:06:38,910 --> 00:06:40,910
N-No, Mother. I'm fine.

61
00:06:40,910 --> 00:06:45,029
Mother, I acted rashly earlier.

62
00:06:45,029 --> 00:06:48,029
But Qiu Shui relies too much
on unorthodox methods.

63
00:06:48,029 --> 00:06:52,550
If he persists, he'll suffer in the martial world.

64
00:06:52,550 --> 00:06:59,110
I hope this lesson should steer him back
to righteous training.

65
00:06:59,110 --> 00:07:01,030
No harm done then.

66
00:07:05,269 --> 00:07:09,189
But Father, I didn't get it.

67
00:07:20,069 --> 00:07:23,469
From now on, the Huanhua Sect's leadership token

68
00:07:23,469 --> 00:07:29,110
shall be kept by Xiao Yi Ren.

69
00:07:39,550 --> 00:07:46,350
But the heir position shall be decided later.

70
00:07:54,389 --> 00:08:01,029
Qiu Shui, you could've dodged
that strike. Why didn't you?

71
00:08:01,029 --> 00:08:04,870
Xi Lou, how could Qiu Shui evade
that sword energy?

72
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:09,589
You think I wouldn't recognize
your Triple Shameless Moves?

73
00:08:09,589 --> 00:08:15,034
He evaded the first two strikes.
He could've evaded the third too.

74
00:08:18,266 --> 00:08:21,230
Qiu Shui, why didn't you evade it?

75
00:08:23,349 --> 00:08:27,549
With Father, Mother, and everyone
behind me, how could I evade it?

76
00:08:29,349 --> 00:08:32,829
Dueling through deceit is wrong.

77
00:08:32,829 --> 00:08:36,550
This duel should be your loss.

78
00:08:36,550 --> 00:08:42,869
But shielding others earned you a reprieve.

79
00:08:42,869 --> 00:08:48,109
So, I make your brother
act as sect leader for now.

80
00:08:48,109 --> 00:08:55,389
In six months, you two will face
each other again in a fair duel.

81
00:08:56,349 --> 00:09:00,069
No, Father. Six months is too long.

82
00:09:00,069 --> 00:09:01,869
I'll...

83
00:09:08,030 --> 00:09:15,230
To lead a sect, if you lack patience for
even half a year, you're unfit.

84
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:20,069
You just walk the path with clear conscience.

85
00:09:20,069 --> 00:09:24,709
What isn't yours yet can't be rushed.

86
00:09:24,709 --> 00:09:30,430
The Huanhua Sect bears all consequences.

87
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:38,710
Qiu Shui.

88
00:09:39,550 --> 00:09:45,789
I was too harsh earlier. Don't hold it against me.

89
00:09:47,109 --> 00:09:49,190
I-I won't.

90
00:09:49,190 --> 00:09:52,710
In six months, let's duel properly.

91
00:09:54,709 --> 00:09:57,869
Supplies are ready. Don't wait any longer.

92
00:09:57,869 --> 00:10:01,390
Proceed to Guangling Villa at once.

93
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:03,470
- Understood.
- Guangling?

94
00:10:06,310 --> 00:10:08,470
Yi Ren. Yi Ren!

95
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:15,950
Lost your sword?

96
00:10:18,630 --> 00:10:20,430
Shattered your blade?

97
00:10:25,109 --> 00:10:27,190
What can you use now?

98
00:10:30,589 --> 00:10:34,350
We have fine swords in storage.

99
00:10:35,310 --> 00:10:37,310
Choose one.

100
00:10:37,310 --> 00:10:43,030
Father, lend me the Sword of Changge.

101
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:44,229
Qiu Shui.

102
00:10:44,229 --> 00:10:46,310
Trying to push your luck?

103
00:10:46,310 --> 00:10:52,109
That's the symbol of the sect leader.
Seeking power already?

104
00:10:52,109 --> 00:10:53,909
N-No, not at all.

105
00:10:57,150 --> 00:11:01,269
Focus on proper training. No more schemes.

106
00:11:03,310 --> 00:11:06,310
Are you okay? Does it hurt?

107
00:11:07,229 --> 00:11:09,029
You're tormenting him.

108
00:11:12,589 --> 00:11:15,470
Rest well. I will check on you later.

109
00:11:18,790 --> 00:11:22,589
Well, well. I'll fetch medicine.

110
00:11:22,589 --> 00:11:24,389
Okay, Xue Yu.

111
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:31,549
You have no choice but to wait now.

112
00:11:37,709 --> 00:11:39,509
I'll endure.

113
00:11:40,190 --> 00:11:44,390
 Xiao Qiu Shui, you keep surprising us. 

114
00:11:44,390 --> 00:11:48,749
 Given time, you'll surpass your father and Yi Ren. 

115
00:11:48,749 --> 00:11:53,149
 Pity. I won't grant the Xiao family that time. 

116
00:11:54,670 --> 00:12:00,670
Yi Ren's Huanhua Swordplay is formidable.
I must avoid direct clashes.

117
00:12:00,670 --> 00:12:02,470
Qiu Shui.

118
00:12:04,109 --> 00:12:06,550
Xue Yu, take a seat.

119
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:10,190
- Is it still hurting?
- It's fine.

120
00:12:10,190 --> 00:12:13,029
I'm going to Guangling Villa with Yi Ren.

121
00:12:14,390 --> 00:12:17,310
Remember to apply these ointments regularly.

122
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:21,469
Thank you, Xue Yu.

123
00:12:21,469 --> 00:12:24,349
Yi Ren actually cares deeply about you.

124
00:12:24,349 --> 00:12:26,430
When he learned I was coming,

125
00:12:26,430 --> 00:12:32,350
though acting indifferent, he mentioned
herbs, hinting me to bring them to you.

126
00:12:34,869 --> 00:12:37,590
I know he means well.

127
00:12:39,190 --> 00:12:43,989
Oh, Mother asked me to bring gifts
from Zihui. Let me fetch them for you.

128
00:12:43,989 --> 00:12:47,349
Qiu Shui, the carriage is ready outside.

129
00:12:47,349 --> 00:12:51,749
Just give me those gifts after I return.

130
00:12:54,150 --> 00:13:01,030
Why this sudden ambition to compete
with Yi Ren for family leadership?

131
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:06,229
Having goals is good anyway.
But don't just pay lip service.

132
00:13:06,229 --> 00:13:11,430
Keep up your training discipline while I'm away.

133
00:13:12,069 --> 00:13:14,190
Got it. Don't worry.

134
00:13:15,229 --> 00:13:21,749
Qiu Shui. Among the younger generation,
Yi Ren truly stands out.

135
00:13:21,749 --> 00:13:23,550
But don't rush yourself.

136
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:29,669
With more experience, our Xiao family
will have another renowned hero.

137
00:13:31,270 --> 00:13:33,109
I understand.

138
00:13:33,109 --> 00:13:40,030
By the way, Xue Yu, don't take
Kang Jie Sheng's words to heart.

139
00:13:40,030 --> 00:13:43,710
Whatever kind of person you choose,
I'll support you.

140
00:13:45,150 --> 00:13:47,749
He must be an upright hero
of unwavering integrity.

141
00:13:47,749 --> 00:13:50,670
He has to be skilled in martial arts
and decisive in actions.

142
00:13:50,670 --> 00:13:55,789
But moral character matters most.
He must be noble-hearted and righteous.

143
00:13:56,869 --> 00:13:59,030
Good.

144
00:13:59,030 --> 00:14:04,510
Xue Yu, your happiness should be
in your own hands.

145
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:07,109
No one should pressure you.

146
00:14:07,109 --> 00:14:08,869
Alright, I get it.

147
00:14:08,869 --> 00:14:11,630
Practice diligently during this period.

148
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:16,350
In six months, I'll join Master Qiu Shui
in roaming the martial world.

149
00:14:18,869 --> 00:14:20,550
I must depart now.

150
00:14:20,550 --> 00:14:24,669
Take care of yourself. Don't upset
our parents. Understood?

151
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:39,470
Xiao Qiu Shui, come out!

152
00:14:44,749 --> 00:14:48,190
Yi Ren, Kai Yan? Xue Yu said you'd already left.

153
00:14:48,190 --> 00:14:50,510
Eager to see us gone?

154
00:14:50,510 --> 00:14:52,829
You're not even seeing us off to Guangling.

155
00:14:52,829 --> 00:14:54,669
So eager to be rid of us?

156
00:14:56,229 --> 00:14:58,590
My head feels dizzy.

157
00:14:59,349 --> 00:15:02,230
Yi Ren's got something to tell you.

158
00:15:08,229 --> 00:15:12,190
After we leave, properly care
for Father and Mother.

159
00:15:12,190 --> 00:15:16,310
Obey them. Don't make them upset. Understood?

160
00:15:19,589 --> 00:15:21,270
That hurts?

161
00:15:21,270 --> 00:15:22,829
No.

162
00:15:22,829 --> 00:15:27,589
Still resent Yi Ren?

163
00:15:27,589 --> 00:15:29,229
Not really.

164
00:15:29,229 --> 00:15:33,669
Rest assured. I'll take good care of them.

165
00:15:40,310 --> 00:15:43,550
Train hard while we're away.

166
00:15:43,550 --> 00:15:47,590
We'll have a proper duel when we return.

167
00:15:50,349 --> 00:15:53,630
Stay out of trouble. No mischief.

168
00:15:53,630 --> 00:15:55,390
Let's go.

169
00:15:55,390 --> 00:15:59,469
- Be good.
- Yi Ren, Kai Yan, stay safe.

170
00:15:59,469 --> 00:16:01,269
We will.

171
00:16:08,910 --> 00:16:10,710
 Greetings. 

172
00:16:14,229 --> 00:16:16,589
How's everything?

173
00:16:16,589 --> 00:16:19,790
All forces near Chuanjin
have been mobilized to Jin City.

174
00:16:19,790 --> 00:16:21,709
Awaiting your command.

175
00:16:21,709 --> 00:16:25,670
Using Fu Tian Yi's vengeance as pretext,
we'll isolate the Xiaos.

176
00:16:25,670 --> 00:16:28,069
The Sword King?

177
00:16:28,069 --> 00:16:31,470
No movement since Purple Phoenix's ambush.

178
00:16:33,469 --> 00:16:38,550
Keep alert. Stop him
from meddling with the Hero Token.

179
00:16:38,550 --> 00:16:40,229
Understood.

180
00:16:40,229 --> 00:16:42,778
Madam Wu has taken refuge in Sword Retreat.

181
00:16:44,550 --> 00:16:46,869
They've noticed?

182
00:16:46,869 --> 00:16:51,030
It's fine. You just
drive the Xiaos to desperation.

183
00:16:51,030 --> 00:16:54,509
I'll breach Sword Retreat and find her myself.

184
00:16:54,509 --> 00:16:57,469
Shall we inform others about your presence?

185
00:16:57,469 --> 00:17:00,509
They don't know you. I fear it might disturb you.

186
00:17:00,509 --> 00:17:02,590
They lack that capability.

187
00:17:02,590 --> 00:17:08,430
Remember this. Show no mercy to the Xiaos.

188
00:17:11,309 --> 00:17:13,309
Annihilate them completely.

189
00:17:14,910 --> 00:17:16,710
Understood.

190
00:17:19,117 --> 00:17:22,593
 

191
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:27,430
- Get me some noodles.
- Coming right up.

192
00:17:28,949 --> 00:17:32,910
Some tea first, please.

193
00:17:34,309 --> 00:17:36,109
Wonderful.

194
00:17:37,190 --> 00:17:39,870
Excuse me. Where's the Huanhua Sect?

195
00:17:39,870 --> 00:17:43,870
Oh, there? South along this road
leads to the Xiaos of the Huanhua Sect.

196
00:17:43,870 --> 00:17:45,749
- Come take a look.
- Good.

197
00:17:45,749 --> 00:17:46,949
Thank you.

198
00:17:46,949 --> 00:17:49,069
Your noodles will be ready soon.

199
00:17:49,949 --> 00:17:55,829
 With Tang Rou as my excuse, I can get
into the Xiaos to find the Hero Token. 

200
00:18:02,070 --> 00:18:04,069
What's happening here?

201
00:18:05,309 --> 00:18:07,589
It's broad daylight. What's going on?

202
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:12,430
What bad luck.

203
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:14,110
Bad luck.

204
00:18:14,110 --> 00:18:15,150
Let me see.

205
00:18:15,150 --> 00:18:16,950
Let me see.

206
00:18:19,029 --> 00:18:20,749
Can't figure anything out.

207
00:18:20,749 --> 00:18:21,805
Power Gang?

208
00:18:21,805 --> 00:18:23,802
 

209
00:18:28,350 --> 00:18:31,350
- This...
- A coffin?

210
00:18:31,350 --> 00:18:33,150
Go take a look.

211
00:18:37,326 --> 00:18:39,830
 

212
00:18:39,830 --> 00:18:45,430
 Xiao Qiu Shui's sword?
The Power Gang targets the Xiaos. 

213
00:18:55,190 --> 00:18:58,469
 
 Power Gang will attack? 

214
00:18:58,469 --> 00:19:00,990
 They found out. 

215
00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:04,910
Father! Mother!

216
00:19:04,910 --> 00:19:07,590
Qiu Shui, why the panic?

217
00:19:07,590 --> 00:19:10,670
Father, Mother, I...

218
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:25,070
The weather's fine these days,
just right for a trip to the mountains.

219
00:19:25,070 --> 00:19:29,390
How about we go out sometime soon?
What do you think?

220
00:19:30,509 --> 00:19:34,870
What are you scheming now?

221
00:19:34,870 --> 00:19:39,150
Qiu Shui, what's going on?

222
00:19:39,150 --> 00:19:40,830
Father.

223
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:41,830
Xiao Qiu Shui!

224
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:44,390
Sis! Sis!

225
00:19:44,390 --> 00:19:46,430
Sis! Sis!

226
00:19:47,269 --> 00:19:50,509
Xiao Qiu Shui, tell Tang Rou
to leave the Xiao residence immediately.

227
00:19:50,509 --> 00:19:55,749
Don't drag my brother into your mess.
The Power Gang's blood coffin is here.

228
00:19:58,390 --> 00:20:03,029
The Power Gang's blood coffins?
It means they're seeking vengeance.

229
00:20:03,029 --> 00:20:06,230
Master Xiao.

230
00:20:06,949 --> 00:20:11,110
Power Gang's blood coffins were found in Jin City.

231
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:14,870
The coffin contains Mr. Qiu Shui's sword.

232
00:20:22,910 --> 00:20:25,829
- You may leave.
- Understood.

233
00:20:28,029 --> 00:20:30,190
Wasn't that sword disposed of?

234
00:20:31,029 --> 00:20:34,430
Qiu Shui, when did you cross the Power Gang?

235
00:20:35,269 --> 00:20:38,870
 What can I do? I burned it. 

236
00:20:38,870 --> 00:20:43,549
Qiu Shui, tell me everything.

237
00:20:57,670 --> 00:21:03,269
- Qiu Shui killed Iron Demon Fu Tian Yi?
- Three years ago, Huizhou's Fuhu Blade

238
00:21:03,269 --> 00:21:05,759
seized a Power Gang pawnshop.

239
00:21:05,759 --> 00:21:09,509
Twelve people were killed overnight.

240
00:21:09,509 --> 00:21:14,509
Heluo's Tongding Sect feuded
with them over port ownership.

241
00:21:14,509 --> 00:21:17,910
Their entire clan was executed.
Bodies dumped in rivers.

242
00:21:17,910 --> 00:21:23,910
Cross the Power Gang, and this is
your fate. They won't show mercy.

243
00:21:33,150 --> 00:21:37,670
If they want revenge,
they should come for me alone.

244
00:21:37,670 --> 00:21:41,830
What matters most now is that
everyone leaves Huanhua at once.

245
00:21:41,830 --> 00:21:45,350
Father, Mother, I'll protect you.

246
00:21:45,350 --> 00:21:47,456
What can you do?

247
00:21:47,456 --> 00:21:50,070
Qiu Shui.

248
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:57,585
Where's your proof of collusion between
Jinyin Bank and Wastelanders?

249
00:21:57,585 --> 00:22:00,630
 

250
00:22:00,630 --> 00:22:02,589
Father, see for yourself.

251
