colluding with outsiders.

259
00:22:40,762 --> 00:22:44,109
Why fear revenge for righteous action?

260
00:22:45,709 --> 00:22:51,579
Today, my third son executed a traitor.

261
00:22:51,579 --> 00:22:55,910
This brings honor to the Xiao family.

262
00:22:55,910 --> 00:23:02,390
Our family bears responsibility
for any consequences.

263
00:23:02,390 --> 00:23:08,190
You're all uninvolved in this. Please leave now.

